    <entry>
      <title>Hit-OSLab environment on WSL2</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/08/hitoslab_enri/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/08/hitoslab_enri/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>在我搭建Hit-OSLab的过程中，我发现在WSL2上搭建该环境的教程并不多，对于像我这样的WSL使用者来说并不友好，因此我决定记录一下我在WSL2上搭建Hit-OSLab的过程，希望能帮助到更多的人。</p></blockquote><h3 id="1-首先下载linux0-11"><a href="#1-首先下载linux0-11" class="headerlink" title="1. 首先下载linux0.11"></a>1. 首先下载linux0.11</h3><p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1ZmGW92s994c-KooVVce7HQ">百度网盘链接</a><br>提取码：yang</p><p>在本地解压后复制到wsl</p><h3 id="2-安装依赖"><a href="#2-安装依赖" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装依赖"></a>2. 安装依赖</h3><p>我已将需要安装的依赖整理在了一个脚本中，可以直接运行</p><p>新建一个文件夹tools,在里面新建脚本文件enri.sh,将下面的内容复制进去</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install lib32ncurses6 lib32z1</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libsm6:i386</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libx11-6:i386</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libxpm4:i386</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libc6-dev-i386</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install bin86</span><br><span class="line">wget http://old-releases.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/g/gcc-3.4/gcc-3.4-base_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --force-depends -i gcc-3.4-base_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://old-releases.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/g/gcc-3.4/gcc-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --force-depends -i gcc-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb </span><br><span class="line">wget http://old-releases.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/g/gcc-3.4/cpp-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --force-depends -i cpp-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb </span><br><span class="line">wget http://old-releases.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/g/gcc-3.4/g++-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --force-depends -i g++-3.4_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">wget http://old-releases.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/pool/universe/g/gcc-3.4/libstdc++6-dev_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo dpkg --force-depends -i libstdc++6-dev_3.4.6-6ubuntu3_amd64.deb</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install make</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install libgtk2.0-0 libxss1 libasound2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install qemu-user-static</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-binfmts --install i386 /usr/bin/qemu-i386-static --magic <span class="string">&#x27;\x7fELF\x01\x01\x01\x03\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00\x00\x03\x00\x03\x00\x01\x00\x00\x00&#x27;</span> --mask <span class="string">&#x27;\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xfc\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xf8\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff\xff&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>键入该命令运行脚本即可自行安装所有环境</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sh enri.sh </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-编译linux0-11"><a href="#3-编译linux0-11" class="headerlink" title="3. 编译linux0.11"></a>3. 编译linux0.11</h3><p>安装之后在终端进入linux0.11目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/oslab/linux0.11</span><br><span class="line">$ make</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样整个环境就安装好了，但别急，由于wsl的特殊性，我们还需要为其加上一个窗口，这样才能打开我们的bochs捏😋</p><h3 id="4-安装窗口"><a href="#4-安装窗口" class="headerlink" title="4. 安装窗口"></a>4. 安装窗口</h3><p>既然wsl缺少窗口，那么我们安装一个就好力，这里我们选择<a href="%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5%EF%BC%9Ahttps://sourceforge.net/projects/vcxsrv/">VcXsrv</a>,安装到Windows即可</p><p>安装完按照默认设置打开即可。</p><p>配置wsl参数，在终端中输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果你使用的是 WSL 1</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;export DISPLAY=:0.0&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; .profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果你使用的是 WSL 2：填入 &#123;YOUR_WINDOWS_IP&#125;，你的本机 IP 地址</span></span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="string">&#x27;export DISPLAY=&#123;YOUR_WINDOWS_IP&#125;:0.0&#x27;</span> &gt;&gt; .profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后安装一个小眼睛👀，检查一下图形窗口是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo apt install x11-apps -y &amp;&amp; xeyes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果出现了一个小眼睛，那么恭喜你，你已经成功安装了图形窗口。</p><p>但是，当你走到这一步时，你会发现事情显然没有这么简单，这样的一条报错信息会出现在你的终端中</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Error: Can&#x27;t open display: </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>问题大概出在WSL2会在首次启动时创建一个虚拟网卡用于提供 WSL2 的网络，默认情况下这个ip是动态的(本人太菜，不是很懂，若有错误请指正😢)</p><p>下面是解决方案</p><ul><li><p>1 打开控制面板\系统和安全\Windows Defender 防火墙\允许应用通过 Windows 防火墙<br>更改设置→勾选<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210419233714570.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzQyNDcxNDIz,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="网络设置"></p></li><li><p>2 在Windows的cmd中切换到VcXsrv所在目录，通过命令行添加参数启动vcxsrv(非常重要的一步，也是我觉得最麻烦的一步，由于本人水平有限，目前只会这样解决，请见谅)</p></li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ .\vcxsrv.exe -ac -terminate -lesspointer -multiwindow -clipboard -wgl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>3 将前文echo命令的内容改为</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> DISPLAY=`grep nameserver /etc/resolv.conf | sed <span class="string">&#x27;s/nameserver //&#x27;</span>`:0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成上述步骤后，再去执行安装小眼睛的命令，就可以看到小眼睛了。</p><h3 id="5-回到终端打开linux0-11目录，即可运行"><a href="#5-回到终端打开linux0-11目录，即可运行" class="headerlink" title="5. 回到终端打开linux0.11目录，即可运行"></a>5. 回到终端打开linux0.11目录，即可运行</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ../run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行后即可看到你的系统，就可以开始实验了！</p>]]></content>
      
      
